Big Brother Naija, BBNaija 2020, housemate, Erica, has said that Kiddwaya is her “special friend.” Erica stated this during the post-eviction interview with show host, Ebuka Obi-Uchendu. When asked about the love triangle between her and Kiddwaya and Laycon, she replied: “Kiddwaya is my special friend. He is my bestie.” Erica also asked Laycon, who also has feelings for her to “keep his distance.” In response, Laycon said: “I think it will be better for both of us if I keep my distance. “It will not be easy, but I think that is what is best.” DAILY POST reports that Big Brother apologized for interfering in the love episode between the three housemates.